     and reelect a list of size n, such that the value of the component at exponent i be the factorial of i if i is even 
     or the sum of act from 1 to i otherwise. 
     i begin from 1. 
     the factorial of i is the multiplication of the number from 1 to i (1 * 2 *... * i).
